Package: bellit
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: libnotify-bin
Description: Cross-platform CLI tool for sending desktop notifications
 Bell It sends native desktop notifications from the terminal, either
 immediately or after a long-running command has completed. It can also use
 terminal OSC notification sequences when running through SSH or tmux.
